lue":"картофельная мука"},{"lang":"cs","value":"bramborová mouka"},{"lang":"de","value":"Kartoffelmehl"},{"lang":"en","value":"potato flour"},{"lang":"es","value":"Harina de patata"},{"lang":"fa","value":"آرد سيب‌زميني"},{"lang":"fr","value":"farine de pomme de terre"},{"lang":"hi","value":"आलू का आटा"},{"lang":"hu","value":"burgonyaliszt"},{"lang":"it","value":"Fecola di patata"},{"lang":"ja","value":"ジャガイモ粉、ジャガイモデンプン、バレイショ粉"},{"lang":"pl","value":"Mąka ziemniaczana"},{"lang":"pt","value":"farinha de batata"}],"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#prefLabel":[{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_be_a2296771"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_pt-BR_e245ed96"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_sw_157722cd"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ar_bc91a590"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ka_d6f11116"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_nb_80b52e75"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ro_83a059a8"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_tr_35681_1321794578762"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_zh_1299487531244"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_th_1299487531207"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_sk_1299487531009"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ru_1299487530973"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_pt_1299487530941"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_pl_1299487530910"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ja_1299487530881"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_it_1299487530853"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_hu_1299487530828"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_hi_1299487530804"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_fr_1299487530783"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_fa_1299487530740"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_es_1299487530720"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_en_1299487530702"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_de_1299487530686"},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_cs_1299487530670"}]},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_5157454a","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO. 2008. https://www.fao.org/4/i0500c/i0500c02.pdf","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:55:00"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"zh","value":"另外一种脱水产品是用煮熟并碾碎的整马铃薯制作的马铃薯粉,它保留了薯独特的味道。马铃薯粉无麸质并富含淀粉,它被食品业用于搅拌肉馅以及使汤增稠。"}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_8a2add22","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO. 2008. https://www.fao.org/4/i0500a/i0500a02.pdf","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:58:47"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"ar","value":"وهناك منتج آخر مجفف هو دقيق البطاطا الذي يتم طحنه من بطاطا كاملة مطهية ويبقى محتفظا بطعم البطاطا المميز. وتستخدم صناعات الأغذية هذا الدقيق الخالي من الغلوتين والغني بالنشا كمادة رابطة في خلطات اللحوم. وكذلك لزيادة كثافة صلصات مرق اللحم والشوربات ويذكر."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_b79dbc43","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO, 2008. La papa. https://www.fao.org/4/i0500s/i0500s02.pdf","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:49:26"},"dct:modified":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:51:41"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"es","value":"La harina de papa se obtiene de la papa cocida entera y mantiene un sabor característico. La industria alimentaria utiliza la harina de papa, que no contiene gluten pero sí abundante almidón, para aglutinar productos compuestos de diversos tipos de carnes e impartir espesor a salsas y sopas."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_bb65e90a","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO. 2008. The Potato. https://www.fao.org/4/i0500e/i0500e02.pdf","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:47:07"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"en","value":"Potato flour is ground from cooked, whole potatoes and retains a distinct potato taste. Gluten-free and rich in starch, potato flour is used by the food industry to bind meat mixtures and thicken gravies and soups."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_d06d052c","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO, 2008. Картофель. https://www.fao.org/4/i0500r/i0500r02.pdf","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:51:21"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"ru","value":"Картофельную муку, получают из вареных целых картофелин, она сохраняет присущий картофелю вкус. Не содержащая клейковины и богатая крахмалом картофельная мука используется в пищевой промышленности, чтобы связывать мясные смеси и сгущать соусы и супы."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_e92ac560","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO, 2008. La pomme de terre. https://www.fao.org/4/i0500f/i0500f02.pdf","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-11-28T08:48:32"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"fr","value":"On obtient la farine de pomme de terre, par broyage de tubercules entiers qui sont précuits et conservent le goût de la pomme de terre. Cette farine, sans gluten et riche en amidon, est utilisée par l’industrie alimentaire comme liant des produits carnés et pour épaissir les sauces et les soupes"}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ar_bc91a590","type":"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#Label","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2021-09-21T11:56:42Z"},"http://rdfs.org/ns/void#inDataset":{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/void.ttl#Agrovoc"},"skos:notation":{"type":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/AgrovocCode","value":"35681"},"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/sko